item.title: CVE-2022-32145|2024-08-03T07:32:55.971Z -- siemens -- teamcenter%20active%20workspace%20v5.2
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Teamcenter Active Workspace V5.2 (All versions < V5.2.9), Teamcenter Active Workspace V6.0 (All versions < V6.0.3). A reflected cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exists in the web interface of the affected application that could allow an attacker to execute malicious code by tricking users into accessing a malicious link.
